        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "工业相机 _ 成像器",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            41,
            22,
            400,
            88
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CCD (Charge Coupled Device)_ 电荷耦合装置",
        "bbox": [
            27,
            201,
            627,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CCD 目前的技术比较成熟，但其工艺复杂、成本高、耗电量大、像素提升难度大。",
        "bbox": [
            27,
            266,
            908,
            342
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CMOS (Complementary Metal Oxide Semiconductor) ",
        "bbox": [
            27,
            488,
            697,
            531
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "_ 互补金属氧化物半导体",
        "bbox": [
            83,
            548,
            391,
            592
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CMOS 由于制造工艺简单，因此可以在普通半导体生产线上进行生产，其制造成本相对比较低廉。",
        "bbox": [
            27,
            614,
            909,
            688
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "COGNEX SUPERHEROES 2013 ",
        "bbox": [
            827,
            5,
            991,
            164
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "footer",
        "text": "COGNEX ",
        "bbox": [
            804,
            909,
            945,
            938
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "10 ",
        "bbox": [
            51,
            962,
            65,
            977
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "footer",
        "text": "| Confidential $\\circledcirc$ 2012 Cognex Corporation ",
        "bbox": [
            69,
            962,
            275,
            981
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "工业相机 _ 主要参数",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            41,
            22,
            444,
            88
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ". 4. 曝光方式 (Exposure) 和快门方式 (Shutter) ：",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            26,
            177,
            563,
            218
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "线阵相机都是逐行曝光的方式，可以选择固定行频和外触发同步的采集方式，曝光时间可以与行周期一致，也可以设定一个固定的时间；面阵工业相机有帧曝光、场曝光和滚动行曝光等几种常见方式，工业相机机一般都提供外触发采图的功能。快门速度一般可到 10 微秒，高速工业相机还可以更快。",
        "bbox": [
            25,
            238,
            933,
            392
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "5. 像元尺寸 (Pixel Size) ：",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            26,
            412,
            334,
            451
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "像元大小和像元数 ( 分辨率 ) 共同决定了相机机靶面的大小。目前数字工业相机像元尺寸一般为 3μm-10μm ，一般像元尺寸越小，制造难度越大，图像质量也越不容易提高。 (1/3’:7.4X7.4μm 1/1.8’:4.4X4.4μm)",
        "bbox": [
            25,
            472,
            933,
            587
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "table",
        "img_path": "images/498eae7b7ef6a979f52373c0cd96cf9123bf0dd127c339f8ded77ce541ef442b.jpg",
        "table_caption": [],
        "table_footnote": [],
        "table_body": "<table><tr><td></td><td>1英寸</td><td>2/3英寸</td><td>1/2英寸</td><td>1/3英寸</td><td>1/4英寸</td></tr><tr><td>对角线(mm)</td><td>16</td><td>11</td><td>8</td><td>6</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>幅面尺(mm)</td><td>12.8×9.6</td><td>8.8×6.6</td><td>6.4×4.8</td><td>4.8×3.6</td><td>3.6×2.7</td></tr></table>",
        "bbox": [
            177,
            600,
            745,
            705
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "? 6. 光谱响应特性 (Spectral Range) ：",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            26,
            729,
            448,
            768
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "指该像元传感器对不同光波的敏感特性，一般响应范围是 350nm －1000nm 。",
        "bbox": [
            26,
            788,
            844,
            864
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "COGNEX SUPERHEROES 2013 ",
        "bbox": [
            827,
            5,
            991,
            164
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
